keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Genetic.Shared.Genotypes

Class GenotypeFuzzyGAP

  • java.lang.Object
    • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Genetic.Shared.Genotypes.Genotype
      • keel.Algorithms.Fuzzy_Rule_Learning.Genetic.Shared.Genotypes.GenotypeFuzzyGAP

  • public class GenotypeFuzzyGAP
extends Genotype

    GenotypeFuzzyGAP is the base clase to represent the genotype when a fuzzy model is to be learned with the genetic algorithm and programming (GAP). Both the constants and the tree node are learned. The Fuzzy model variables are characterized with FuzzyPartitions. The root node is a NodeRuleBase.

    Since:
    JDK1.4

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Written by Luciano Sanchez (University of Oviedo) 20/01/2004, Modified by J.R. Villar (University of Oviedo) 18/12/2008
